# TC38 : ObstacleDetectedBoost5
# Related normal-mode case : TC28_ObstacleDetected5
# Precondition : BoostMode, forward=false
# Action : right obstacle detected, front/left clear
# Expected : BoostMode 유지, CleanerDriver mode=boost 유지, turnLeft, forward=true
power
start
dust
expect mode BoostMode
expect cleaner on
expect cleanerMode boost
obstacle 1 1 1
expect mode BoostMode
expect cleanerMode boost
expect motorForward false
obstacle 0 0 1
expect mode BoostMode
expect cleaner on
expect cleanerMode boost
expect motor moving
expect motorForward true
expect motorDirection LEFT
exit
